original_sql: SELECT ps.ps_comment AS ps_ps_comment, MIN(r.r_name) AS min_r_r_name, MAX(ps.ps_suppkey) AS max_ps_ps_suppkey, MAX(ps.ps_supplycost) AS max_ps_ps_supplycost, COUNT(ps.ps_availqty) AS count_ps_ps_availqty FROM partsupp ps, region r WHERE r.r_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_name FROM part WHERE p_size > 20 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_brand FROM (SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 8 ) UNION ALL SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_size > 15) t GROUP BY p_brand ORDER BY p_brand) AND ps.ps_availqty > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_custkey) FROM (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 2000 UNION ALL SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 3000) t JOIN nation ON n_nationkey = t.o_custkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_name FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation) AS u_4 JOIN orders ON u_4.c_name = o_orderstatus) AND EXISTS (SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty > 75 ) UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 75 ) ORDER BY s_name) AND ps.ps_partkey > 86171 AND ps.ps_partkey < 136803 AND ps.ps_suppkey > 5400 AND ps.ps_suppkey < 8332 AND ps.ps_availqty > 407 AND ps.ps_availqty < 8545 AND ps.ps_supplycost > 604.9211642304817 AND ps.ps_supplycost < 994.8928577595344 AND r.r_regionkey > 1 AND r.r_regionkey < 1  GROUP BY ps.ps_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT AVG(p.p_partkey) AS avg_p_p_partkey, COUNT(p.p_size) AS count_p_p_size, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment, COUNT(s.s_acctbal) AS count_s_s_acctbal, p.p_comment AS p_p_comment FROM part p, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' ) UNION SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate < '1995-01-01' ) ORDER BY c_name) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT ps_availqty FROM partsupp UNION SELECT l_quantity FROM lineitem UNION SELECT l_quantity FROM (SELECT DISTINCT l_quantity FROM lineitem AS l1_2 WHERE l_shipdate < '1995-01-01') AS subq_2) AND s.s_acctbal > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_address FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_address FROM supplier ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT MAX(s_acctbal) FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey BETWEEN 1 AND 5 ) t GROUP BY s_nationkey ORDER BY s_nationkey) AND p.p_mfgr IN (SELECT DISTINCT p_mfgr FROM part UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier AS s1_5 WHERE s_acctbal < 5000) AS subq_5) AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000005515%' AND p.p_partkey < 16219 AND p.p_name LIKE 'bisque antique orange misty pale%' AND p.p_size > 49 AND p.p_container LIKE 'SM PKG%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'LARGE BRUSHED TIN%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#2%' AND s.s_nationkey > 15 AND s.s_suppkey >= 8624 AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#21%'  GROUP BY p.p_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT p.p_mfgr AS p_p_mfgr, MIN(p.p_mfgr) AS min_p_p_mfgr, AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_p_p_retailprice, MAX(p.p_container) AS max_p_p_container, COUNT(p.p_comment) AS count_p_p_comment FROM part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION SELECT p_container FROM part UNION SELECT p_container FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_container FROM part AS p1_1 WHERE p_size > 5) AS subq_1) AND EXISTS (SELECT o_orderstatus FROM (SELECT o_orderstatus, o_orderdate FROM orders ) AS subq_2 UNION SELECT n_comment FROM nation) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_brand FROM (SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1996-12-31' UNION SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.1) UNION ALL SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_returnflag = 'A' UNION ALL SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipmode = 'TRUCK')) t GROUP BY p_brand) AND EXISTS (SELECT s_4.s_phone FROM supplier s_4 WHERE s_4.s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_4.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps_4 WHERE ps_4.ps_supplycost > 150 UNION ALL SELECT ps2_4.ps_suppkey FROM partsupp ps2_4 WHERE ps2_4.ps_availqty > 200 GROUP BY ps2_4.ps_suppkey) AND s_4.s_acctbal < 4000) AND p.p_mfgr IN (SELECT p_mfgr FROM (SELECT p_mfgr, p_size FROM part WHERE p_size = 10 ) AS subq_5 WHERE p_size > 9 ORDER BY p_size) AND p.p_partkey > 161005 AND p.p_partkey < 178790 AND p.p_name LIKE 'seashell dim light navajo blush%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#5%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#44%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'STANDARD ANODIZED BRASS%' AND p.p_size > 27 AND p.p_size < 28 AND p.p_container LIKE 'WRAP PACK%' AND p.p_retailprice < 1318.4503718162937  GROUP BY p.p_mfgr LIMIT 50;

SELECT COUNT(l.l_comment) AS count_l_l_comment, MIN(l.l_comment) AS min_l_l_comment, MAX(l.l_partkey) AS max_l_l_partkey, SUM(l.l_discount) AS sum_l_l_discount, COUNT(c.c_address) AS count_c_c_address FROM customer c, lineitem l, nation n WHERE n.n_name IN (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name, n_regionkey FROM nation ) AS subq_1 UNION SELECT p_container FROM part) AND EXISTS (SELECT l_linestatus FROM (SELECT l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey IN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1997-01-01' ) UNION ALL SELECT l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax > 0.02) t GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND EXISTS (SELECT n_comment FROM (SELECT n_comment FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 3000 UNION SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 2000) UNION ALL SELECT n_comment FROM nation WHERE n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION ALL SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_phone LIKE '30%')) t GROUP BY n_comment) AND l.l_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1500 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1996-01-01') AS subq_4 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_4.o_custkey) AND c.c_comment IN (SELECT c_comment FROM (SELECT c_comment, c_nationkey FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 5 ) AS subq_5 WHERE c_nationkey > 4 ORDER BY c_nationkey) AND n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey AND n.n_regionkey > 2 AND c.c_custkey <= 119772 AND l.l_tax = 0.02747559329872846 AND l.l_discount < 0.055878172004113984 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'FOB%' AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'R%' AND n.n_name LIKE 'EGYPT%' AND c.c_nationkey >= 21 AND l.l_suppkey <= 4621 AND l.l_shipdate > '1994-01-31'  LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(p.p_type) AS count_p_p_type, MAX(p.p_name) AS max_p_p_name, MIN(p.p_partkey) AS min_p_p_partkey, MAX(p.p_type) AS max_p_p_type, MIN(p.p_retailprice) AS min_p_p_retailprice FROM part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT n_name FROM (SELECT n_name, n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 1 ) AS subq_1 WHERE n_regionkey > 0 ORDER BY n_regionkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT s_comment FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_comment FROM supplier AS s1_2 WHERE s_acctbal > 3000) AS subq_2) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem UNION SELECT l_returnflag FROM (SELECT DISTINCT l_returnflag FROM lineitem AS l1_3 WHERE l_quantity > 20) AS subq_3) AND p.p_retailprice = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders JOIN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION ALL SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000) AS cust_union_4 ON orders.o_custkey = cust_union_4.c_custkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT p_type FROM (SELECT p_type, COUNT(*) FROM part GROUP BY p_type HAVING COUNT(*) > 6) AS subq_5) AS t_5) AND p.p_partkey > 20680 AND p.p_partkey < 25973 AND p.p_name LIKE 'cornflower navajo indian bisque dark%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#3%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#42%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'PROMO PLATED TIN%' AND p.p_size > 3 AND p.p_size < 4 AND p.p_container LIKE 'MED CASE%' AND p.p_retailprice <= 2047.6190918105565  LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(p.p_partkey) AS count_p_p_partkey, MAX(p.p_partkey) AS max_p_p_partkey, MIN(o.o_clerk) AS min_o_o_clerk, COUNT(p.p_type) AS count_p_p_type, COUNT(p.p_container) AS count_p_p_container FROM orders o, part p WHERE EXISTS (SELECT SUM(l_extendedprice) FROM (SELECT l_extendedprice, l_returnflag FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE o_orderpriority = '1-URGENT' UNION SELECT l_extendedprice, l_returnflag FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE o_orderstatus = 'F' AND o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000)) AS subq_1 GROUP BY l_returnflag) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity < 10 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1997-01-01')) AS subq_2 GROUP BY o_orderpriority) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part UNION SELECT s_phone FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_phone FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_phone FROM supplier AS s1_3 WHERE s_nationkey = 3) AS subq_3) AND p.p_retailprice = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_brand FROM part UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND o.o_totalprice IN (SELECT DISTINCT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION SELECT DISTINCT c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.18) AND p.p_partkey = 72505 AND p.p_retailprice = 1303.1123915382427 AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#5%' AND o.o_orderkey > 4244010 AND o.o_totalprice > 549233.7504660367 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'F%' AND p.p_type LIKE 'MEDIUM POLISHED BRASS%' AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#13%' AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '4-NOT SPECIFIED%' AND o.o_orderdate <= '1993-02-09'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT MIN(n.n_comment) AS min_n_n_comment, COUNT(l.l_partkey) AS count_l_l_partkey, COUNT(l.l_quantity) AS count_l_l_quantity, MAX(l.l_linestatus) AS max_l_l_linestatus, COUNT(l.l_receiptDATE) AS count_l_l_receiptDATE FROM lineitem l, nation n, region r WHERE EXISTS (SELECT AVG(l_quantity) FROM (SELECT l_quantity, l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1995-03-01' UNION ALL SELECT l_quantity, l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate <= '1995-03-01' GROUP BY l_quantity, l_linestatus) t JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey, o_totalprice FROM orders) o ON t.l_quantity = o.o_orderkey GROUP BY o.o_totalprice) AND EXISTS (SELECT SUM(l_extendedprice) FROM (SELECT l_extendedprice, l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE o_orderpriority = '2-HIGH' UNION SELECT l_extendedprice, l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem JOIN orders ON l_orderkey = o_orderkey WHERE o_orderstatus = 'P' AND o_custkey IN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 500)) AS subq_2 GROUP BY l_shipinstruct) AND r.r_comment IN (SELECT DISTINCT r_comment FROM region UNION SELECT p_comment FROM part UNION SELECT p_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_comment FROM part AS p1_3 WHERE p_retailprice > 100) AS subq_3) AND n.n_name IN (SELECT DISTINCT n_name FROM nation UNION SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION SELECT c_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT c_name FROM customer AS c1_4 WHERE c_acctbal < 2000) AS subq_4) AND l.l_extendedprice > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem ) t) AND n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey AND r.r_name LIKE 'AMERICA%' AND n.n_regionkey <= 3 AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'A%' AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'SHIP%' AND l.l_commitdate > '1993-09-03' AND r.r_regionkey = 3 AND l.l_tax = 0.0670204000646908 AND l.l_suppkey > 6445 AND l.l_receiptdate > '1996-04-05' AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT MIN(c.c_nationkey) AS min_c_c_nationkey, COUNT(s.s_comment) AS count_s_s_comment, COUNT(s.s_phone) AS count_s_s_phone, SUM(s.s_suppkey) AS sum_s_s_suppkey, SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS sum_s_s_acctbal FROM customer c, supplier s WHERE c.c_phone IN (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone, c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal = 1000 ) AS subq_1 WHERE c_acctbal > 500 ORDER BY c_acctbal) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_mfgr FROM part UNION SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier AS s1_2 WHERE s_acctbal < 5000) AS subq_2) AND c.c_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n_nationkey) FROM nation JOIN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 3000 UNION ALL SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_comment LIKE '%excellent%') AS subq_3 ON nation.n_nationkey = subq_3.s_nationkey) AND s.s_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM (SELECT p_partkey, p_name FROM part WHERE p_size > 20 ) t) AND c.c_acctbal = (SELECT (16 * 4) + COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part WHERE p_container IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_returnflag = 'N')) AND c.c_custkey > 70643 AND c.c_custkey < 93986 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000015893%' AND c.c_nationkey > 3 AND c.c_nationkey < 18 AND c.c_acctbal > 62.695729400134496 AND c.c_acctbal < 6944.497417126958 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'HOUSEHOLD%' AND s.s_suppkey > 3896 AND s.s_suppkey < 5020  LIMIT 50;

SELECT AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_c_c_acctbal, COUNT(o.o_comment) AS count_o_o_comment, MAX(c.c_mktsegment) AS max_c_c_mktsegment, MIN(c.c_phone) AS min_c_c_phone, MAX(o.o_comment) AS max_o_o_comment FROM customer c, orders o, region r WHERE EXISTS (SELECT l_shipmode FROM (SELECT l_shipmode, l_orderkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_orderkey = 8 ) AS subq_1 WHERE l_orderkey > 7 ORDER BY l_orderkey) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_partkey FROM part UNION SELECT ps_partkey FROM (SELECT ps_partkey, COUNT(*) FROM partsupp GROUP BY ps_partkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 3) AS subq_2) AS t_2) AND c.c_name IN (SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_custkey IN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01' UNION SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal > 1000) AND c_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation JOIN region ON n_regionkey = r_regionkey WHERE r_name = 'ASIA')) AND r.r_comment IN (SELECT DISTINCT r_comment FROM region UNION SELECT p_comment FROM part UNION SELECT p_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_comment FROM part AS p1_4 WHERE p_retailprice > 100) AS subq_4) AND o.o_custkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 3) UNION ALL SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 300) t) AND c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey AND o.o_custkey < 61834 AND o.o_orderpriority LIKE '4-NOT SPECIFIED%' AND o.o_orderkey < 74702 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000022237%' AND c.c_acctbal <= 8326.917235693052 AND o.o_orderstatus LIKE 'P%' AND r.r_name LIKE 'AMERICA%' AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'HOUSEHOLD%' AND c.c_custkey > 1572 AND o.o_orderdate <= '1994-04-20'  LIMIT 50;

SELECT COUNT(l.l_tax) AS count_l_l_tax, MAX(l.l_receiptDATE) AS max_l_l_receiptDATE, MAX(l.l_discount) AS max_l_l_discount, MIN(l.l_extendedprice) AS min_l_l_extendedprice, SUM(l.l_quantity) AS sum_l_l_quantity FROM lineitem l WHERE EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM supplier UNION SELECT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT p_name FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part AS p1_1 WHERE p_size > 10) AS subq_1) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_name FROM part UNION SELECT s_comment FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT s_comment FROM supplier AS s1_2 WHERE s_acctbal > 3000) AS subq_2) AND EXISTS (SELECT MIN(ps_supplycost) FROM (SELECT ps_supplycost, ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 30 ) t GROUP BY ps_suppkey ORDER BY ps_suppkey) AND l.l_orderkey IN (SELECT DISTINCT l_orderkey FROM lineitem UNION SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01') AND l.l_suppkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_size) FROM part JOIN (SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp UNION ALL SELECT ps_partkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 10) AS partsupp_union_5 ON part.p_partkey = partsupp_union_5.ps_partkey) AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'SHIP%' AND l.l_shipinstruct LIKE 'DELIVER IN PERSON%' AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'A%' AND l.l_quantity < 27.754931148728105 AND l.l_extendedprice = 55192.130690681 AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'O%' AND l.l_shipdate <= '1996-12-17' AND l.l_linenumber > 5 AND l.l_receiptdate > '1992-11-27' AND l.l_discount >= 0.021461656160225752  LIMIT 50;

SELECT COUNT(c.c_nationkey) AS count_c_c_nationkey, COUNT(n.n_regionkey) AS count_n_n_regionkey, c.c_comment AS c_c_comment, COUNT(c.c_name) AS count_c_c_name, MIN(c.c_acctbal) AS min_c_c_acctbal FROM customer c, nation n WHERE EXISTS (SELECT MIN(p_retailprice) FROM (SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN partsupp ON p_partkey = ps_partkey WHERE ps_availqty > 100 UNION SELECT p_retailprice, p_brand FROM part JOIN lineitem ON p_partkey = l_partkey WHERE l_quantity > 30 AND l_shipmode IN (SELECT l_shipmode FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate < '1995-01-01')) AS subq_1 GROUP BY p_brand) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone, c_mktsegment FROM customer ) AS subq_2 UNION SELECT p_type FROM part) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_custkey) FROM orders WHERE o_orderstatus = 'O' UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipmode = 'TRUCK' UNION ALL SELECT 0 FROM part WHERE p_size = 15) AND EXISTS (SELECT s_address FROM (SELECT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_name = 'FRANCE' ) UNION ALL SELECT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 1500) t GROUP BY s_address ORDER BY s_address) AND n.n_regionkey = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_address FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT s_address FROM supplier ) t) AND c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND c.c_custkey > 49857 AND c.c_custkey < 82400 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000010993%' AND c.c_nationkey > 7 AND c.c_nationkey < 8 AND c.c_acctbal > 579.938086696581 AND c.c_acctbal < 7564.154061708443 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'AUTOMOBILE%' AND n.n_nationkey > 0 AND n.n_nationkey < 14  GROUP BY c.c_comment LIMIT 50;

SELECT AVG(c.c_custkey) AS avg_c_c_custkey, COUNT(s.s_comment) AS count_s_s_comment, s.s_comment AS s_s_comment, MAX(p.p_container) AS max_p_p_container, COUNT(p.p_retailprice) AS count_p_p_retailprice FROM customer c, part p, supplier s WHERE s.s_address IN (SELECT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost > 200 ) UNION SELECT s_address FROM supplier WHERE s_suppkey IN (SELECT ps_suppkey FROM partsupp WHERE ps_supplycost < 200 ) ORDER BY s_address) AND c.c_phone IN (SELECT c_phone FROM (SELECT c_phone, c_acctbal FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal = 1000 ) AS subq_2 WHERE c_acctbal > 500 ORDER BY c_acctbal) AND p.p_partkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_name) FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal > 8000 EXCEPT SELECT c_name FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 1500 ) AS subquery_3) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1996-01-01' ) UNION SELECT p_name FROM part WHERE p_partkey IN (SELECT l_partkey FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate < '1996-01-01' ) ORDER BY p_name) AND s.s_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_linenumber) FROM lineitem JOIN (SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT o_orderkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1995-01-01') AS order_union_5 ON lineitem.l_orderkey = order_union_5.o_orderkey) AND p.p_retailprice < 2095.6344131659716 AND c.c_acctbal < -882.8973257780403 AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000005287%' AND p.p_partkey < 182349 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000005682%' AND p.p_mfgr LIKE 'Manufacturer#4%' AND p.p_container LIKE 'SM PKG%' AND s.s_acctbal > 3023.055094890745 AND p.p_brand LIKE 'Brand#44%' AND s.s_nationkey <= 4  GROUP BY s.s_comment LIMIT 100;

SELECT SUM(s.s_suppkey) AS sum_s_s_suppkey, ps.ps_supplycost AS ps_ps_supplycost, COUNT(ps.ps_suppkey) AS count_ps_ps_suppkey, s.s_phone AS s_s_phone, MIN(ps.ps_comment) AS min_ps_ps_comment FROM nation n, partsupp ps, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT o_1.o_clerk FROM orders o_1 WHERE o_1.o_orderkey IN (SELECT l_1.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l_1 WHERE l_1.l_discount > 0.05 UNION ALL SELECT l2_1.l_orderkey FROM lineitem l2_1 WHERE l2_1.l_shipdate < DATE '1995-06-01' GROUP BY l2_1.l_orderkey) AND o_1.o_totalprice < 5000) AND s.s_address IN (SELECT DISTINCT s_address FROM supplier UNION SELECT s_phone FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 10) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(p_size) FROM (SELECT p_size, p_type FROM part WHERE p_size < 15 ) t GROUP BY p_type ORDER BY p_type) AND ps.ps_suppkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT n_nationkey) FROM nation JOIN (SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_acctbal < 2000 UNION ALL SELECT s_nationkey FROM supplier WHERE s_comment LIKE '%reliable%') AS subq_4 ON nation.n_nationkey = subq_4.s_nationkey) AND n.n_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT o_totalprice FROM orders UNION ALL SELECT l_extendedprice FROM lineitem ) t) AND ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey AND s.s_suppkey = 1551 AND ps.ps_availqty = 6835 AND n.n_name LIKE 'IRAQ%' AND ps.ps_supplycost >= 917.7278237825307 AND s.s_acctbal <= -288.4995139071207 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000004460%' AND ps.ps_partkey >= 146548 AND ps.ps_suppkey > 9327 AND n.n_regionkey <= 1 AND n.n_nationkey <= 15  GROUP BY s.s_phone, ps.ps_supplycost LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(s.s_nationkey) AS count_s_s_nationkey, MIN(s.s_nationkey) AS min_s_s_nationkey, MAX(s.s_nationkey) AS max_s_s_nationkey, MAX(n.n_comment) AS max_n_n_comment, MAX(n.n_regionkey) AS max_n_n_regionkey FROM nation n, supplier s WHERE EXISTS (SELECT SUM(l_discount) FROM (SELECT l_discount, l_linestatus FROM lineitem WHERE l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1998-01-01' AND DATE '1998-12-31' ) t GROUP BY l_linestatus ORDER BY l_linestatus) AND s.s_suppkey > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer JOIN (SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_totalprice > 1500 UNION ALL SELECT o_custkey FROM orders WHERE o_orderdate > '1996-01-01') AS subq_2 ON customer.c_custkey = subq_2.o_custkey) AND n.n_regionkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT p_size FROM part UNION ALL SELECT l_quantity FROM lineitem ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT l_shipmode FROM lineitem UNION SELECT p_container FROM part UNION SELECT p_container FROM (SELECT DISTINCT p_container FROM part AS p1_4 WHERE p_size < 15) AS subq_4) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT s_name FROM (SELECT s_name FROM supplier UNION ALL SELECT p_name FROM part) AS u_5 JOIN lineitem ON u_5.s_name = l_shipmode) AND n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey AND n.n_nationkey > 10 AND n.n_nationkey < 19 AND n.n_name LIKE 'JORDAN%' AND n.n_regionkey > 2 AND n.n_regionkey < 3 AND s.s_suppkey > 1530 AND s.s_suppkey < 7991 AND s.s_name LIKE 'Supplier#000006668%' AND s.s_nationkey > 12 AND s.s_nationkey < 20  LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(l.l_commitDATE) AS count_l_l_commitDATE, COUNT(l.l_discount) AS count_l_l_discount, MIN(l.l_orderkey) AS min_l_l_orderkey, MIN(l.l_receiptDATE) AS min_l_l_receiptDATE, AVG(l.l_tax) AS avg_l_l_tax FROM lineitem l WHERE l.l_tax > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT r_regionkey) FROM region WHERE r_name = 'EUROPE' AND (r_regionkey = 1 OR r_regionkey = 2) AND 9+9=18 AND r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name = 'GERMANY' AND 10*11=110)) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_mktsegment FROM customer UNION SELECT DISTINCT r_name FROM region WHERE r_regionkey = 1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_size > 12) AND l.l_partkey > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT p_name FROM part ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT p_4.p_type FROM part p_4 WHERE p_4.p_partkey IN (SELECT l_4.l_partkey FROM lineitem l_4 WHERE l_4.l_quantity > 30 UNION ALL SELECT l2_4.l_partkey FROM lineitem l2_4 WHERE l2_4.l_extendedprice < 500 GROUP BY l2_4.l_partkey) AND p_4.p_size > 10) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(o_orderkey) FROM (SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN customer ON o_custkey = c_custkey WHERE c_mktsegment = 'AUTOMOBILE' UNION SELECT o_orderkey, o_orderpriority FROM orders JOIN lineitem ON o_orderkey = l_orderkey WHERE l_quantity < 10 AND l_shipdate IN (SELECT l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_receiptdate > '1997-01-01')) AS subq_5 GROUP BY o_orderpriority) AND l.l_quantity >= 39.301274964494986 AND l.l_partkey < 136954 AND l.l_orderkey <= 3714402 AND l.l_extendedprice > 44655.42266309608 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'SHIP%' AND l.l_discount = 0.09098550679059658 AND l.l_linestatus LIKE 'F%' AND l.l_shipdate <= '1994-03-19' AND l.l_receiptdate < '1997-07-07' AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'A%'  LIMIT 10;

SELECT MAX(c.c_acctbal) AS max_c_c_acctbal, COUNT(c.c_phone) AS count_c_c_phone, SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS sum_c_c_acctbal, c.c_acctbal AS c_c_acctbal, AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_ps_ps_supplycost FROM customer c, nation n, partsupp ps WHERE c.c_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_suppkey) FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax < 0.05 AND (l_returnflag = 'A' OR l_returnflag = 'R') AND l_commitdate > '1996-01-01') AND ps.ps_availqty = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o_orderkey) FROM orders JOIN (SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING' UNION ALL SELECT c_custkey FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 500) AS cust_union_2 ON orders.o_custkey = cust_union_2.c_custkey) AND c.c_acctbal > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c_custkey) FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 3000 AND (c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE' OR c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD') AND c_phone LIKE '30%') AND n.n_nationkey = (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM nation WHERE n_regionkey = 3) AND s_acctbal < 3000 AND s_phone LIKE '27%') AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_acctbal FROM customer UNION SELECT s_acctbal FROM (SELECT s_acctbal, COUNT(*) FROM supplier GROUP BY s_acctbal HAVING COUNT(*) > 5) AS subq_5) AS t_5) AND c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey AND ps.ps_availqty = 3086 AND ps.ps_supplycost >= 656.857574263646 AND n.n_nationkey > 6 AND c.c_mktsegment LIKE 'MACHINERY%' AND c.c_name LIKE 'Customer#000000303%' AND c.c_acctbal <= 3151.6093341046144 AND c.c_nationkey = 10 AND ps.ps_suppkey < 2066 AND n.n_regionkey = 0 AND c.c_custkey >= 23117  GROUP BY c.c_acctbal LIMIT 50;

SELECT s.s_phone AS s_s_phone, COUNT(s.s_address) AS count_s_s_address, MIN(ps.ps_partkey) AS min_ps_ps_partkey, COUNT(s.s_comment) AS count_s_s_comment, MAX(s.s_comment) AS max_s_s_comment FROM partsupp ps, supplier s WHERE ps.ps_supplycost > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT c_name FROM customer UNION ALL SELECT n_name FROM nation ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_phone FROM customer UNION SELECT c_address FROM customer WHERE c_nationkey = 15) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT c_comment FROM customer UNION SELECT l_comment FROM lineitem UNION SELECT l_comment FROM (SELECT DISTINCT l_comment FROM lineitem AS l1_3 WHERE l_tax < 0.05) AS subq_3) AND s.s_acctbal > (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT l_orderkey) FROM (SELECT l_orderkey, l_shipdate FROM lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 10 ) t) AND EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT o_orderpriority FROM orders UNION SELECT DISTINCT c_mktsegment FROM customer WHERE c_acctbal < 1000 UNION SELECT DISTINCT l_shipinstruct FROM lineitem WHERE l_tax > 0.1) AND ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey AND ps.ps_partkey > 15996 AND ps.ps_partkey < 131582 AND ps.ps_suppkey > 8538 AND ps.ps_suppkey < 8671 AND ps.ps_availqty > 803 AND ps.ps_availqty < 9489 AND ps.ps_supplycost > 583.5043969971737 AND ps.ps_supplycost < 735.2264972023686 AND s.s_suppkey > 3909 AND s.s_suppkey < 8066  GROUP BY s.s_phone LIMIT 10;

SELECT MIN(l.l_linenumber) AS min_l_l_linenumber, MIN(l.l_returnflag) AS min_l_l_returnflag, MIN(l.l_tax) AS min_l_l_tax, COUNT(l.l_comment) AS count_l_l_comment, AVG(l.l_orderkey) AS avg_l_l_orderkey FROM lineitem l WHERE EXISTS (SELECT DISTINCT p_mfgr FROM part UNION SELECT p_brand FROM part WHERE p_retailprice < 50) AND EXISTS (SELECT r_comment FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name LIKE 'E%' ) UNION SELECT r_comment FROM region WHERE r_regionkey IN (SELECT n_regionkey FROM nation WHERE n_name NOT LIKE 'E%' ) ORDER BY r_comment) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT s_suppkey FROM supplier UNION SELECT l_suppkey FROM (SELECT l_suppkey, COUNT(*) FROM lineitem GROUP BY l_suppkey HAVING COUNT(*) > 15) AS subq_3) AS t_3) AND EXISTS (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT p_partkey) FROM part WHERE p_size > 10 UNION ALL SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT ps_suppkey) FROM partsupp WHERE ps_availqty < 1000 UNION ALL SELECT 0 FROM supplier WHERE s_nationkey = 4) AND l.l_returnflag IN (SELECT DISTINCT l_returnflag FROM (SELECT l_returnflag FROM lineitem UNION ALL SELECT o_orderstatus FROM orders) AS u_5 JOIN customer ON u_5.l_returnflag = c_phone) AND l.l_receiptdate >= '1997-04-17' AND l.l_suppkey <= 8251 AND l.l_returnflag LIKE 'N%' AND l.l_discount = 0.054120840734448554 AND l.l_partkey >= 19951 AND l.l_shipmode LIKE 'FOB%' AND l.l_quantity = 16.97314089478435 AND l.l_linenumber = 2 AND l.l_extendedprice > 45866.71217688886 AND l.l_tax = 0.037942568050421864  LIMIT 30;
